Package: TukeyGH77
Type: Package
Title: Tukey g-&-h Distribution
Version: 0.2.0
Description: Density, cumulative density, quantile and
       simulation of the 4-parameter Tukey g-and-h (1977) distributions. The
       quantile-based transformation (Hoaglin 1985
       <doi:10.1002/9781118150702.ch11>) and its reverse
       transformation, as well as the letter-value based estimates
       (Hoaglin 1985).
